    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this activity is for students to solve a real-world problem involving area. The activity includes a rectangle where the side lengths are labeled. When students solve problems with multiple solutions and have to choose and justify a solution, they make sense of problems and persevere in solving them (MP1). In their small groups and in the class discussion students have an opportunity to explain and defend their choices (MP3).</p>
